{"tid":538152,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[親情台]大家激嬲細佬妹會點哄？","createTime":"2018-01-23T11:17:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-23T12:59:45.000Z","uid":136658,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"01c22b907205f0814fb5582b4512264f5480e793","tid":538152,"uid":136658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T11:17:29.000Z","msg":"同細佬爭1年 鬧親交都隔一陣好翻<br />\n同細妹就爭9年 好少鬧交 <br />\n因為佢多數同細佬鬧<br />\n我唔加把口幫是但一邊都唔會惹屎上身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過前日細妹唔知黎M定乜<br />\n佢叫我出去幫佢買野食 但佢已經食左飯<br />\n話突然好想食 我又整梗野 就話唔出 <br />\n佢又發脾氣 我就梗係鬧翻佢<br />\n之後佢就開始人身攻擊 大家都知對方最介意啲乜 就偏偏要鬧嗰樣野 <br />\n自己都覺得嗰陣講既野好難聽 有啲後悔<br />\n<br />\n重點 到今日佢都仲嬲梗 <br />\n我講sorry又好odd 未試過咁薑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n通常第二日就好翻<br />\n<br />\n請教各位巴絲點哄細佬妹又唔odd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74fdd9dd73642ffb0a808423303022a9b3c6afa6","tid":538152,"uid":136658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T11:20:49.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d00ad5122c42d1d313fc5c26ba642a121b86e64e","tid":538152,"uid":86433,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T11:21:56.000Z","msg":"00後真係比樓主呢類人搞成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7cea4a626f069bcf194c9771812f225a3b81bb3","tid":538152,"uid":113165,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T11:22:30.000Z","msg":"打柒佢"},{"pid":"2ffb551be6546c4898f091c5d2ce88cde4d92861","tid":538152,"uid":158245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T11:22:56.000Z","msg":"要哄?過2日就冇野"},{"pid":"4c43165fb18423b1a1faed699ca539ebf96104e5","tid":538152,"uid":97431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T11:24:47.000Z","msg":"兜巴星落去"},{"pid":"45befa691399119248fde1fb82f4965e7afdbe8d","tid":538152,"uid":139873,"like":0,"dis